synonym.mean: 页；记录；大事件，时期；男侍者

pos_mean_info_list.mean: 用传呼机传呼（page的现在分词形式）

word_group.brief_definition: (经过困难后)翻开新的一页, 开始新的生活
目标一致, 就目标达成共识
页面布局；页布局；网页布局

bilingual.source: Look at the two pictures on this page.
bilingual.target: 看看这一页上的两张图片。
学生们重读学生用书的那一页。

bilingual.source: Turn to Page 87 to find out your result.
bilingual.target: 翻到第87页查看你的结果。

bilingual.source: Each unit contains three, two-page lessons.
bilingual.target: 每个单元包含三个两页的课程。

bilingual.source: The pictures on this page show famous leaders.
bilingual.target: 这页上的图片展示了著名的领导人。

bilingual.source: Which pictures on these page could be of a circus?
bilingual.target: 这页上的哪些图片可能是马戏团的？

bilingual.source: This page from the Internet makes the game sound fun.
bilingual.target: 这页来自互联网的内容让游戏听起来很有趣。

bilingual.source: Go to the map page of the website and find your beach.
bilingual.target: 进入网站的地图页面并找到你的海滩。

bilingual.source: If possible, make a web page for your gallery after class.
bilingual.target: 如果可能，下课后为你的画廊制作网页。

list.abstract: Page为计算机编程语言指令，用来定义JSP文件中的全局属性。
page在互联万维网上，是指一个网页，就是一个用超文本链接标示语言（HTML）符号标记的文档；在电脑的随机存储内存（RAM）中，是一组存储单元，是可以独立运行的部分；在使用虚拟内存（也称为虚位存储）的计算机系统里，是数据存储单元。

yingyinNormal.en: Someone joined our page. We have an actual fan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但有人加了我们的粉丝页，我们有一个粉丝了。

yingyinNormal.en: Now I'd like you to turn to page 1. Now I'd like you to read from page 1 to 48.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在请翻回到第1页，现在请大家从第1页读到第48页。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, fine. I'm checking her Facebook page.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我是在看她的主页。

yingyinNormal.en: That's not an email. That's Leslie's Facebook page.
yingyinNormal.zh: 才不是邮件呢，你在看莱斯利的FACEBOOK主页。

yingyinNormal.en: So I'd like you guys to open your books to page 48.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请大家把书翻到48页。

yingyinNormal.en: I just need one page. Which page can we use? News, sports, fashion. Not the fashion page. OK, I'll use the business page.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只需要一张纸。哪页是我们不要的？新闻版，体育版，噢对了，时尚版。不要用我的时尚版。好吧，那我们就用商业版。

yingyinNormal.en: My first 10 page paper, they didn't assign those in my high school.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的第一份十页论文，高中没人会布置这么长的作业。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, there were a lot of pictures, and one page only had the word "Brakkadoom!"
yingyinNormal.zh: 大部分都只是图片啊，有一页上甚至只写了一句"受死吧"。

yingyinNormal.en: Word of warning page 73. I don't understand. It makes no sense. It looks impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 提醒一下，是第73页的。我完全不明白，说不通啊，不可能啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, this is cool. So, a few weeks ago, I set up a fan page on Facebook for our band and...
yingyinNormal.zh: 这挺酷，几周前呢，我在脸书上给我们乐团开了个粉丝页...

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, so for tonight's assignment, I'd like you to write me a three-page essay on anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听好，今晚的家庭作业是请大家写一篇三页的论文，题目不限。

yingyinNormal.en: Page 14, item seven. So, what's for dinner? A side of corn succotash. Hmm. Interesting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第14页，第7条。那么我们到底吃什么？一份豆煮玉米。真有意思。

yingyinNormal.en: What I wanted to talk about was how on page 1 of your book, you say you had hard time not bringing your work home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想说的是，在你书的第一页，你为什么会说很难不把工作带回家做呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Without you here to shame me, I watched every Real Housewives episode and I only got to page two in War And Peace.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有你在旁边取笑我，我已堕落到看完全部《贵妇的真实生活》，正经书却才看了两页。

yingyinNormal.en: This is not happening. Be that as it may, page nine says that you have to provide me with lemon-flavored sparkling waters, so chop-chop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是真的。即便是这样，第九页写着你得为我提供柠檬味的气泡水，所以赶紧的…

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, hold on. Page 18 of the surrogacy contract, Tara, you specifically agreed to terminate if there were substantial signs of birth defects.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，冷静点，代孕合同第18页，塔拉你特别同意了若有足够证据证明孩子先天缺陷则终止妊娠。

yingyinNormal.en: From 'Rule Britannia' to 'Cool Britannia', the fabric and the skyline of this city is forever turning over a new page, which is, after all, what every great story should do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从「大不列颠的统治」到「大不列颠的风格」，这个城市的高楼大厦和建筑正不断地揭开新的一页，这正是所有伟大城市的必经过程。

yingyinNormal.en: Is that guy on your Facebook page, is he gonna be there? Who?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你脸书主页上的那个人也会去吗？谁？

yingyinNormal.en: That light means it's on? It doesn't automatically turn off when you go to a different web page?
yingyinNormal.zh: 亮灯表示开着吗？我关掉网页时摄像头不会自动关掉吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Penny? Well, it's a little juvenile. I mean, it kind of looks like the MySpace page of a 13-year-old girl.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮？呃，有一点点幼稚，看着像一个13岁女孩的个人主页。

examination_example.sentence: While there's little innovation when it comes to passport cover color, the same cannot be said for the <highlight>pages</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然护照封面的颜色没有什么创新，但内页就不一样了。

examination_example.sentence: Believe it or not, I had a full notebook of magazine <highlight>pages</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 信不信由你，我有一本铺满杂志页的笔记本。

examination_example.sentence: She checked the index and turned over to a <highlight>page</highlight> about early Chinese immigrants in California.

examination_example.sentence: To date, his online <highlight>page</highlight> to raise funds has brought in more than $44,000 and counting, raising more than $17,000 in just one day.

word_usage.usage:
表示“第几页”时，可以使用“page+基数词/阿拉伯数字”，也可以使用“the+基数词+page”的结构。
如：page ten/10 = the tenth page 第十页
